"""Adaptive clamp: cap max lift based on deficit distribution shape.

Strategy: compute max_lift but cap at Q75 + k*IQR to reject outlier tiles.
This behaves like maxlift when distribution is tight (no outliers) but
like lq<1 when a single tile has extreme deficit.
"""
